class=\"css-1xxlsgn ewf2cv0\"><span class=\"num\">44,428</span><span class=\"unit\">pt</span></span></li><li class=\"e1jtukx00 css-w1rca4 ex3haug0\"><span class=\"css-cjsdul ehnruze0\">9</span><a class=\"user-name css-0 e10qwino0\" href=\"/u/18844797\"><span class=\"css-14dzdfy e1bokax20\"><img src=\"https://d2jtsb989t238a.cloudfront.net/p/18844797/1780800498/small\" alt=\"パトン🆘はる姐🎨🕶️#アート女子\" class=\"thumb-img\" loading=\"lazy\"></span><span class=\"css-qrjx5q ejhaeu10\">パトン🆘はる姐🎨🕶️#アート女子</span></a><span class=\"css-1xxlsgn ewf2cv0\"><span class=\"num\">33,240</span><span class=\"unit\">pt</span></span></li><li class=\"e1jtukx00 css-w1rca4 ex3haug0\"><span class=\"css-cjsdul ehnruze0\">10</span><a class=\"user-name css-0 e10qwino0\" href=\"/u/18252666\"><span class=\"css-14dzdfy e1bokax20\"><img src=\"https://d2jtsb989t238a.cloudfront.net/p/18252666/1782497064/small\" alt=\"ちはる🐮🍀#アート女子 \" class=\"thumb-img\" loading=\"lazy\"></span><span class=\"css-qrjx5q ejhaeu10\">ちはる🐮🍀#アート女子 </span></a><span class=\"css-1xxlsgn ewf2cv0\"><span class=\"num\">32,316</span><span class=\"unit\">pt</span></span></li><li class=\"e1jtukx00 css-w1rca4 ex3haug0\"><span class=\"css-cjsdul ehnruze0\">11</span><a class=\"user-name css-0 e10qwino0\" href=\"/u/18861106\"><span class=\"css-14dzdfy e1bokax20\"><img src=\"https://d2jtsb989t238a.cloudfront.net/p/18861106/1780237045/small\" alt=\"パトンMaYU🫧#アート女子\" class=\"thumb-img\" loading=\"lazy\"></span><span class=\"css-qrjx5q ejhaeu10\">パトンMaYU🫧#アート女子</span></a><span class=\"css-1xxlsgn ewf2cv0\"><span class=\"num\">17,380</span><span class=\"unit\">pt</span></span></li><li class=\"e1jtukx00 css-w1rca4 ex3haug0\"><span class=\"css-cjsdul ehnruze0\">12</span><a class=\"user-name css-0 e10qwino0\" href=\"/u/18846561\"><span class=\"css-14dzdfy e1bokax20\"><img src=\"https://d2jtsb989t238a.cloudfront.net/p/18846561/1781407290/small\" alt=\"ぷれみ🌟🎨パトン投票🙏❗️#アート女子\" class=\"thumb-img\" loading=\"lazy\"></span><span class=\"css-qrjx5q ejhaeu10\">ぷれみ🌟🎨パト